  "summary": "Microsoft OneDrive provider that lets LLM-based apps manage and inspect a user's OneDrive content programmatically. The toolkit exposes operations for file and folder manipulation, sharing, discovery, and user/drive metadata.\n\n**Capabilities**\n- Create, move, copy, and delete files and folders; monitor async operations.\n- Generate and manage share links and access controls.\n- List and search drive contents and enumerate items shared with the user.\n- Retrieve user and drive metadata (quota, owner, environment) for context-aware flows.\n\n**OAuth**\nProvider: microsoft\nScopes: Files.Read, Files.ReadWrite, User.Read"
}